{"tid":1647431,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［戰略討論］和勇一家遍地開花10秒角色鑑定","createTime":"2019-10-11T17:43:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T17:27:18.000Z","uid":282624,"like":46,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"f0781db21829c3ab7871400addc3f97c07f23539","tid":1647431,"uid":282624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T17:43:46.000Z","msg":"叫醒身邊人<br />\n與手足同行<br />\n長期抗爭角色認投<br />\n雖然和勇一家為最終目標<br />\n但礙於心理關口及能力不一<br />\n更因為各派理念分歧<br />\n現階段仍然要分工合作兄弟爬山<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">自認勇武</span></span><br />\n裝修魔法各自選擇<br />\n打狗救人速戰速決<br />\n不被捕不流血為首要考慮<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">自覺偽勇武</span></span><br />\n極限狂奔報哨保護前線<br />\n營造群情洶湧氣氛<br />\n謹守崗位不越軌<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">前線和理非</span></span><br />\n帶備裝備補給遮樽罩漆<br />\n長期遮陣顧己及人<br />\n密切留意各方消息不做解散軍<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中堅和理非</span></span><br />\n湊夠人數最重要<br />\n補給文宣要揸手<br />\n適時散水勿阻塞緊急撤退通道<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">後勤支援</span></span><br />\n遍地開花連儂牆<br />\n高叫口號壯士氣<br />\n保護接走年輕小朋友為主要目標<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">各小朋友各女士男士街坊們</span></span><br />\n今非昔比請好好保護自己<br />\n年齡性別甚至街坊打扮絕非護身符<br />\n時刻留心做好逃生準備勿落單<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">阻膠</span></span><br />\n請眼不見為淨<br />\n<br />\n總原則：兄弟爬山，各有各做；不流血；<span style=\"color: red;\">堅持</span>。<br />\n終極誤解：遍地開花等於遍地裝修遍地魔法，等於危險性極高<br />\n謬誤更正：遍地開花等於<span style=\"color: red;\">全民反抗</span>，各司其職，用自己能力所及方法控訴暴政<br />\n<br />\n利申：冇膽偽勇武<br />\n<br />\n備註：<br />\n戰爭即和平<br />\n自由即奴役<br />\n無知即力量"},{"pid":"b46e113fb8b9a16fb1bcc3554cbf5c09b711943a","tid":1647431,"uid":123956,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T18:23:39.000Z","msg":"備註：<br />\n戰爭即和平<br />\n自由即奴役<br />\n無知即力量<br />\n<br />\n這句出自&lt;1984&gt;用來愚昧人民的說話打出來不解釋做咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n願榮光歸香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92452da8aff7bc2cde2bc028cff3fd53bfede515","tid":1647431,"uid":54262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T18:24:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8afd1eed1e1147ab3fffa7158aab941c7f250047","tid":1647431,"uid":213977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T18:32:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"62d25d20728fa4e6a3d73a6bc431deecd46871f9","tid":1647431,"uid":83025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b46e113fb8b9a16fb1bcc3554cbf5c09b711943a","tid":1647431,"uid":123956,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T18:23:39.000Z","msg":"備註：<br />\n戰爭即和平<br />\n自由即奴役<br />\n無知即力量<br />\n<br />\n這句出自&lt;1984&gt;用來愚昧人民的說話打出來不解釋做咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n願榮光歸香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T18:50:54.000Z","msg":"願榮光歸香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e10cc08eea5917779c54e5ad584a1e17bc82e01e","tid":1647431,"uid":282624,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b46e113fb8b9a16fb1bcc3554cbf5c09b711943a","tid":1647431,"uid":123956,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T18:23:39.000Z","msg":"備註：<br />\n戰爭即和平<br />\n自由即奴役<br />\n無知即力量<br />\n<br />\n這句出自&lt;1984&gt;用來愚昧人民的說話打出來不解釋做咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n願榮光歸香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T19:07:20.000Z","msg":"你唔覺而家同1984一樣樣咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不解釋喺想多啲人去搵下背後意思警剔下"},{"pid":"0f0da75b1ff6d58231641be790d2310bd59bf079","tid":1647431,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T19:48:09.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">全球「和尼畫」<br />\n#XinniethePooh Challenge</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1640322/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1640322/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23XinniethePooh&amp;src=typeahead_click\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsearch%3Fq%3D%2523XinniethePooh%26src%3Dtypeahead_click&d=bDN9RnBWsu2ZFehd%2BUm4uMpe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=522395f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/search?q=%23XinniethePooh&amp;src=typeahead_click</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t0UOaVn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft0UOaVn.png&h=c7fd48b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1yAhQxD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1yAhQxD.png&h=d230a326&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「和尼畫」挑戰<br />\n1.畫出你心中所想的維尼圖<br />\n2.留下你想對習維尼講嘅說話<br />\n3.放上ig、fb、twitter，tag #XinniethePooh<br />\n4.tag 1-3個你想佢一齊畫維尼嘅朋友<br />\n5.被tag嘅朋友一齊畫維尼，讓愛與維尼佔領地球，推到畀習維尼本人見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&quot;Xinnie the Pooh&quot; Challenge<br />\n1. Draw your own &quot;Xinnie the Pooh&quot;<br />\n2. Write down what do you want to tell Chairman Xi<br />\n3. Post your work on ig, fb and twitter with tag #Xinniethepooh <br />\n4. Tag up to 3 more friends to draw together!"},{"pid":"c6a78fa659f2b2a1b75b987eb93bb5e45409ee55","tid":1647431,"uid":264724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0781db21829c3ab7871400addc3f97c07f23539","tid":1647431,"uid":282624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T17:43:46.000Z","msg":"叫醒身邊人<br />\n與手足同行<br />\n長期抗爭角色認投<br />\n雖然和勇一家為最終目標<br />\n但礙於心理關口及能力不一<br />\n更因為各派理念分歧<br />\n現階段仍然要分工合作兄弟爬山<br />\n<br />\n<spa